<plot>Detective James Mercer is no stranger to crime. A fifteen-year veteran of the force, he's seen it all: drugs, prostitution, racketeering and...murder. But when he and his rookie partner stumble upon a fresh case in a Brooklyn apartment, they uncover the deadly (and hilarious) lengths people will go to not to pay rent in New York.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?411707</url></doc>
